1. *Shvatiti* ga je bilo teško. (It was hard to understand him.) 
2. On je *shvatila* da je pogrešio. (He realized he was wrong.)
3. Nisam *shvatio* šta je on mislio. (I didn't understand what he meant.)
4. Ona je *shvatila* da joj je potrebna pomoć. (She realized she needed help.)
5. Nisam mogao da *shvatim* zašto je rekao to. (I couldn't understand why he said that.)
6. Ja sam *shvatio* da je to trebalo da uradim. (I realized I had to do that.)